lopment. The lessons here for the rest of the world are deep and inspiring"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 4120aUniversité de Ngozi. 0aPeace-buildingxStudy and teachingzBurundi. 0aReconciliationxStudy and teachingzBurundi. 0aEthnic conflictzBurundi.1 aNdura-Ouédraogo, Elavie,eauthor.1 aBangayimbaga, Apollinaire,eauthor. 0aRoutledge research in international and comparative education ;v11.  aJZ 5584 B94 T56 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035232030  aJZ 5584 B94 T56 2015wLCc1i0162035232030lON_SHELFmUAAUGp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/4/2015  aJZ 5584 B94 T56 2015wLCc1i0162035247277d10/5/2015e9/30/2015lFLOOR_2mUAEDUCn2p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu3/4/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2014039636bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/309822244